<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>About · Shiōrra · Wellness, Gently Formulated</title>
<meta name="description" content="Shiōrra is a precision wellness brand by K.C. Laboratories — Iron+, Ginger+ and EnergyOne+. Active-form ingredients, clinical doses, gentle on the body. Made in India." />
<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="/img/logo/logo-green.png">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
