    <h1>Wellness, <em>gently formulated</em>.</h1>
    <p>Shiōrra is a holistic wellness brand by <strong>K.C. Laboratories</strong> — a 50-year clinical formulation company headquartered in India. We build one focused product at a time, each grounded in active-form ingredients and the science of how the body actually absorbs them.</p>
