      <span>Est. 2025</span><span class="dot">·</span>
      <span>Mumbai · India</span><span class="dot">·</span>
      <span>3 SKUs &amp; counting</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="s pillars-bg">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="s-head center">
      <span class="s-eyebrow">What we stand for</span>
      <h2 class="s-title">A brand built on <em>four promises</em>.</h2>
      <p class="s-sub">Trust. Science. Inclusion. Guidance. These aren't taglines — they're the filter every product passes through before it earns the Shiōrra name.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillars-grid">
      <div class="pillar-card"><div class="pillar-num">01 · TRUST</div><h4>Clean, real ingredients</h4><p>No preservatives, no artificial colours or flavours. Purity is the starting point, not an afterthought.</p></div>
      <div class="pillar-card"><div class="pillar-num">02 · SCIENCE</div><h4>Active-form first</h4><p>Methylcobalamin, P5P, methylfolate. We pick the form your body can actually use — not the cheapest.</p></div>
      <div class="pillar-card"><div class="pillar-num">03 · INCLUSION</div><h4>For every stage</h4><p>Pregnancy, postpartum, busy adults, active lifestyles. Thoughtful formulation for who you actually are.</p></div>
      <div class="pillar-card"><div class="pillar-num">04 · GUIDANCE</div><h4>Your gentle ally</h4><p>"Shiori" means a guide — a trusted companion. We build products that earn that name, daily.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

