          <h3>Advanced <em>EnergyOne+</em></h3>
          <p>Taurine + Ginseng + B-Complex + minerals + amino acids. Caffeine-free, multi-nutrient support for modern life.</p>
          <span class="prod-card__cta">Explore EnergyOne+ <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></span>
        </div>
